usb: gadget: uvc: add bulk video-streaming endpoint support

Port of the 2022 "usb: gadget: uvc: add bulk transfer support" series
(zju.edu.cn) to 6.6.30, adapted for the Amlogic dwc2 which will not sustain
isochronous IN. Gated on a new configfs attr streaming_bulk_mult (0 = isoc,
nonzero = bulk; bulk uses VS alt-0 only, starts on the COMMIT control, and the
kernel sends no STREAMON event so userspace must start on commit).

